{"tid":396398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"28大字捍衛言論自由 貼嶺大民主牆上遭撕走","createTime":"2017-09-11T15:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T15:39:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6714c2567c68062a661dfab81cc86ce062f9c505","tid":396398,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170911/large/1505137004_de9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170911%2Flarge%2F1505137004_de9f.jpg&h=6356bd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本貼在民主牆左邊的28個大字，變得空空如也。(黎家駒攝)<br />\n<br />\n 大學校園港獨標語風波延伸至嶺南大學！晚上約9時，嶺大校園內學生會民主牆上，28個表達捍衛言論自由的語句，疑遭人惡意破壞撕去，警方接報到場調查。<br />\n<br />\n該28個字的語句，原本以每張A4紙各印一個字，貼在民主牆上，表達：「你不主張香港獨立，亦應捍衛言論自由，縱然立場不同，但應互相尊重」，但結果被人撕掉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170911/57197772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170911%2F57197772&d=Z9oVvM%2FKQPLTnR4gBvc82kjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=5e9ec245\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170911%2F57197772&h=2df816d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170911/57197772</a>"},{"pid":"be9fd7f7d5b73528a593aca50dd863abce7fdc45","tid":396398,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:37:58.000Z","msg":"惡撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f2c12897c67b14916d2490d975d6e59066d246","tid":396398,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"改貼毛主席湖南獨立同毛主席支持言論自由同多黨民主制，應該無人夠膽撕"}]}